  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access Launch Date - Jan 20 2025!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/c4cd7b37d3db8be01ad726bd833d3828.avif?t=1760673191\" width=680 height=250 /></span></p></p><br><h1>2025 RoadMap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/afd1b9bfe9771aa1b527b4f1b4576fcd.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=1367 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/2c24f3083010342e2e2edd2445ee2166.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span>Dive into Aotenjo, where the ancient game of Mahjong meets the strategic depth of deckbuilding. Use unique Artifacts, master intricate Patterns (Yakus), and harness Special Tiles to overcome malicious threats and emerge victorious!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/a0785345ed31313cbfd668350a27b3d0.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/a0785345ed31313cbfd668350a27b3d0.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/a0785345ed31313cbfd668350a27b3d0.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/79454f74586ca560f645ce5385fb7af6.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span>With over 100 Patterns and 144 unique Artifacts, every hand you play can unleash unbelievable combos. Adapt and strategize to use the right gadgets at the right time, or activate the rarest Patterns to turn the tide in your favor.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/6a0c928329fffde82d37fd3013f682d4.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/6a0c928329fffde82d37fd3013f682d4.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/6a0c928329fffde82d37fd3013f682d4.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/082a393fabe9f63b2b004259fd779d02.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span>Aotenjo's levels are seeded to generate new Artifacts, gadgets, and augments each time you play. No two runs are the same, ensuring a fresh and challenging experience with every game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/157bd994e5866d80975fc66199f77d7e.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/157bd994e5866d80975fc66199f77d7e.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/157bd994e5866d80975fc66199f77d7e.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/3289a98b9f9e71ed6b75f499a333061c.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span>Inspired by over 40 different regional Mahjong styles, Aotenjo offers a blend of familiarity and novelty. Whether you’re a beginner or a seasoned player of Richii, MCR, or Cantonese Mahjong, you’ll find something to enjoy. From Two-Suit Only challenges to Dora and Flower Tiles, we have it all!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/0c3ee54406560e253c03386cfac558df.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/0c3ee54406560e253c03386cfac558df.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/0c3ee54406560e253c03386cfac558df.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/e0de6a1e60b347db19ea1920a93fa267.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Artifact Mastery:</strong> Unlock and utilize 144 unique Artifacts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pattern Variety:</strong> Explore and activate 100 different Patterns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Gameplay:</strong> Experience ever-changing levels with seeded generation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different Mahjongs:</strong> Enjoy elements from over 40 regional Mahjong styles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Depth:</strong> Design your strategies and combine all of your Patterns, Tiles, Artifacts and Gadgets to overcome powerful innate threats.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/c7c334b960e3dde74457a90084be5551.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/2c24f3083010342e2e2edd2445ee2166.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span>Dive into Aotenjo, where the ancient game of Mahjong meets the strategic depth of deckbuilding. Use unique Artifacts, master intricate Patterns (Yakus), and harness Special Tiles to overcome malicious threats and emerge victorious!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/a0785345ed31313cbfd668350a27b3d0.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/a0785345ed31313cbfd668350a27b3d0.webm?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/a0785345ed31313cbfd668350a27b3d0.mp4?t=1760673191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/79454f74586ca560f645ce5385fb7af6.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=80 /></span>With over 100 Patterns and 144 unique Artifacts, every hand you play can unleash unbelievable combos. Adapt and strategize to use the right gadgets at the right time, or activate the rarest Patterns to turn the tide in your favor.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/6a0c928329fffde82d37fd3013f682d4.poster.avif?t=1760673191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066570/extras/6a0c928329ff